Buyout Firm Cinven Assessing Mothercare Takeover, Telegraph Says

-- B y   T o n y   C .   D r e i b u s
-- 
2011-12-11T08:50:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-11/buyout-firm-cinven-assessing-mothercare-takeover-telegraph-says.html
Cinven Ltd., the private-equity firm
that owns PizzaExpress, is assessing a 150 million-pound ($235
million) takeover bid for  Mothercare Plc (MTC) , the Sunday Telegraph
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Cinven declined to comment, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tony C. Dreibus in London at 
